casebody.data:
No. 23,

Misc.

Shotkin v. Atchison, Topeka & Santa Fe R. Co. et al. Walter F. Dodd for petitioner. Duke W. Dunbar, Attorney General of Colorado, and Frank A. Wachob, Deputy Attorney General, for Black, District Judge, respondent.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the District Court in and for the City and County of Denver, Colorado, denied for the reason that the application therefor was not made within the time provided by law.
